{
  "texts": [
    "Mishra et al. (2022) conducted fine-tuning on a series of GPT-Neo2.7B causal language models (Black et al., 2021) using LILA, a composite of 20 existing math datasets.",
    "Similarly, Yue et al. (2023) created \"Math-Instruct\", a meticulously curated instruction tuning dataset.",
    "Comprising 13 math datasets with intermediate Chain-of-Thought and Program-of-Thought rationales, this dataset was used to finetune Llama (Touvron et al., 2023a,b; Rozière et al., 2023) models across different scales.",
    "The resulting models demonstrate unprecedented potential in cross-dataset generalization.",
    "Math solver ensemble."
  ]
}